64
00:03:12,447 --> 00:03:13,448
Okay.

65
00:03:20,355 --> 00:03:21,589
How you feelin', Coach?

66
00:03:21,589 --> 00:03:23,158
Excited?

67
00:03:23,158 --> 00:03:24,092
Yeah.

68
00:03:24,092 --> 00:03:25,794
Feeling good. Feeling strong.

69
00:03:25,794 --> 00:03:31,332
