70
00:03:31,332 --> 00:03:32,767
Um...

71
00:03:32,767 --> 00:03:33,868
Listen.

72
00:03:33,868 --> 00:03:35,436
I noticed you've eased up on practice

73
00:03:35,436 --> 00:03:36,905
